# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Datasets & heavy binary artifacts (never commit data to git)
#   SEED / DREAMER raw + derived features live under Data/ and stay local.
#   Root-anchored so it does NOT also ignore the src/eeg_gnn/data package
#   (git is case-insensitive on Windows: bare "Data/" would match "data/").
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/Data/
*.mat
*.pkl
*.npy
*.pth
*.edf

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Regenerable experiment outputs (produced by the training pipeline).
#   Root-anchored (leading /) so these do NOT also ignore tracked source dirs
#   such as scripts/analysis/ or docs/results/ (git is case-insensitive on Windows,
#   so a bare "Analysis/" would otherwise match "scripts/analysis/").
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/Errors/
/Results/
/Params/
/Analysis/
/Analysis_Results/
/Trial_Plots/
/Features/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Reference material / scratch (kept locally, not part of the codebase)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Models_for_EEG_on_the_Datasets/
Dataset_Papers/
GNN_papers/
What_to_do/
OTHER RUNS FOR LATER/
NOTES AND COURSE OF ACTION/

# Heavy exploratory notebooks (kept locally)
GCN_demo.ipynb
preprocessing_EDF.ipynb

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS / editor
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.swp

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Scratch / personal materials at repo root (kept locally, not committed).
# Useful diagrams live in images/ and docs/figures/ (subdirs, not ignored).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/*.pdf
/*.docx
/*.pptx
/*.png
/*.jpg
/program.md
